dc_title_s: Map of Lands in Atlantic City, NJ showing Riparian Commts.
dc_description_s: Map covers area from California Avenue through Beach Thoroughfare.|"Scale: 1 inch = 50 feet|Date: August 1902|Letter attatched to map is to John Payne, Esq. From legal counsel at Thompson E. Cole. Map shows proposed exterior lines for filling as well as some specific coordinates."
